{
  "title": "Turkish Teppan-Cooked Mediterranean Cheese Quesadilla",
  "description": "A savory, cheese-pull monsoon Mediterranean dish featuring paprika and a hint of sweetness, all cooked on an iron teppan.",
  "cuisine": "Turkish",
