  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the iron teppan to medium-high heat.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the garlic, paprika, salt, and pepper.",
    "Brush the teppan with olive oil and add the garlic-paprika mixture.",
    "Place a tortilla on the teppan and sprinkle with feta and mozzarella cheese.",
    "Fold the tortilla in half to enclose the cheese and cook for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Repeat with the remaining tortillas and cheese.",
    "Transfer the cooked quesadillas to a plate and drizzle with honey.",
    "Sprinkle chopped parsley, dill, and mint on top of the quesadillas.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Serve with a side of steamed vegetables or a mixed green salad.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley and dill if desired."
